<section id="blink">
  <h2>data-blink <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">retro</span></h2>
  <p>Text flashes on and off with a step animation, toggling between full and 50% opacity.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Blinking text">{{ blinkCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-blink</code></td><td><code>""</code> (1s), <code>"slow"</code> (2s), <code>"fast"</code> (0.4s)</td><td>Blink rate preset.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>CSS Property</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-blink-rate</code></td><td><code>1s</code></td><td>Duration of one blink cycle.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="blur-reveal">
  <h2>data-blur-reveal <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">effects</span></h2>
  <p>Words start blurred and transition to clear instead of sliding up. Creates a dreamy, focus-pull effect. Triggers on scroll.</p>

  <browser-window src="/docs/examples/demos/blur-reveal-basic.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/blur-reveal" title="Blur Reveal" shadow></browser-window>

  <code-block language="html" label="Blur reveal">{{ blurRevealCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-blur-reveal</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"word"</code>, <code>"line"</code></td><td>Split mode. Default is word.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-blur-reveal-delay</code></td><td>ms</td><td>Stagger delay between chunks (default 80).</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="bounce">
  <h2>data-bounce <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">kawaii</span></h2>
  <p>Spring-loaded bounce animation on hover. Uses elastic easing that overshoots slightly before settling.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Bounce hover">{{ bounceCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-bounce</code></td><td>boolean</td><td>Enables the bouncy hover effect.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="flipboard">
  <h2>data-flipboard <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">retro</span></h2>
  <p>Split-flap departure board effect. Each character sits in a dark cell with a horizontal hinge and cycles through random letters before settling on the target. Requires JS.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Flipboard">{{ flipboardCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-flipboard</code></td><td>boolean</td><td>Enables the split-flap effect on the element's text content.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>CSS Property</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-flip-ms</code></td><td><code>60ms</code></td><td>Duration of each character flip animation.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="glitch">
  <h2>data-glitch <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">effects</span></h2>
  <p>Chromatic aberration glitch with cyan/red channel splitting via CSS pseudo-elements. Tiny JS sets a <code>data-glitch-text</code> attribute for the pseudo-element content.</p>

  <browser-window src="/docs/examples/demos/glitch-basic.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/glitch" title="Glitch Text" shadow></browser-window>

  <code-block language="html" label="Glitch text">{{ glitchCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-glitch</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"hover"</code></td><td>Always-on or hover-triggered.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="gradient-text">
  <h2>data-gradient-text</h2>
  <p>CSS-only gradient coloring with theme-aware defaults and preset palettes. Add <code>data-gradient-text-animate</code> for a flowing animation.</p>

  <browser-window src="/docs/examples/demos/gradient-text-basic.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/gradient-text" title="Gradient Text" shadow></browser-window>

  <code-block language="html" label="Gradient text">{{ gradientCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-gradient-text</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"sunset"</code>, <code>"ocean"</code>, <code>"forest"</code>, <code>"neon"</code></td><td>Gradient preset. Empty uses theme primary&rarr;secondary.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-gradient-text-animate</code></td><td>boolean</td><td>Enable flowing gradient animation.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="hard-shadow">
  <h2>data-hard-shadow <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">retro</span></h2>
  <p>Hard-edged offset text shadows with no blur. Choose single, double, or long trailing shadows with optional color presets. Sets <code>font-weight: 900</code>.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Hard shadow">{{ hardShadowCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-hard-shadow</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"double"</code>, <code>"long"</code></td><td>Shadow depth style.</td></tr>
      <tr><td>(color) <code>red</code>, <code>blue</code>, <code>gold</code>, <code>green</code></td><td>space-separated</td><td>Shadow color preset. Combine with style.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>CSS Property</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-shadow-color</code></td><td><code>oklch(20% 0 0)</code></td><td>Shadow color.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-shadow-offset</code></td><td><code>3px</code></td><td>Base shadow offset distance.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="highlight">
  <h2>data-highlight</h2>
  <p>Animated underline, box fill, or circle highlight that draws in when scrolled into view.</p>

  <browser-window src="/docs/examples/demos/highlight-basic.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/highlight" title="Highlight Draw" shadow></browser-window>

  <code-block language="html" label="Highlight draw">{{ highlightCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-highlight</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"underline"</code>, <code>"box"</code>, <code>"circle"</code></td><td>Highlight style. Default is underline.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-highlight-color</code></td><td>CSS color</td><td>Override color (default: currentColor).</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="marquee">
  <h2>data-marquee <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">retro</span></h2>
  <p>Continuously scrolling horizontal content with edge masking. Children animate left (or right with <code>reverse</code>) in an infinite loop.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Marquee">{{ marqueeCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-marquee</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"reverse"</code>, <code>"slow"</code> (40s), <code>"fast"</code> (8s), <code>"pause"</code></td><td>Direction, speed, or paused state.</td></tr>
      <tr><td>(modifier) <code>hover-pause</code></td><td>space-separated</td><td>Pause animation on hover.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>CSS Property</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-marquee-speed</code></td><td><code>20s</code></td><td>Scroll animation duration.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-marquee-gap</code></td><td><code>var(--size-xl, 3rem)</code></td><td>Gap between repeating items.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="neon">
  <h2>data-neon <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">retro</span></h2>
  <p>Glowing neon text with a pulsing text-shadow halo that breathes in and out over 2.5 seconds.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Neon text">{{ neonCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-neon</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"pink"</code>, <code>"cyan"</code>, <code>"green"</code>, <code>"amber"</code>, <code>"red"</code></td><td>Neon color preset. Empty uses theme primary.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>CSS Property</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-neon-color</code></td><td>Per preset</td><td>The glow color in OKLCH.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-neon-spread</code></td><td><code>0.04em</code></td><td>Glow blur radius.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="outline">
  <h2>data-outline <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">retro</span></h2>
  <p>Hollow outlined text with transparent fill using <code>-webkit-text-stroke</code>. Gracefully skipped via <code>@supports</code>.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Outline text">{{ outlineCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-outline</code></td><td><code>""</code> (1px), <code>"thick"</code> (2px), <code>"ultra"</code> (3px), <code>"glow"</code></td><td>Stroke width or glow mode.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>CSS Property</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-outline-width</code></td><td><code>1px</code></td><td>Stroke width.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-outline-color</code></td><td><code>var(--color-text)</code></td><td>Stroke color.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="particles">
  <h2>data-particles <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">kawaii</span></h2>
  <p>JS-driven floating particle effect. Spawns emoji characters (&#x2726; &#x2727; &#x22C6; &#x2661; &#x2606;) that float upward and fade out. Requires JS.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Particles">{{ particlesCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-particles</code></td><td>boolean</td><td>Enables floating particle spawning.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="rainbow">
  <h2>data-rainbow <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">retro</span></h2>
  <p>Continuous hue-rotation filter that cycles through the full color spectrum.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Rainbow cycling">{{ rainbowCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-rainbow</code></td><td><code>""</code> (4s), <code>"slow"</code> (8s), <code>"fast"</code> (1.5s)</td><td>Cycle speed preset.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>CSS Property</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>--vb-rainbow-speed</code></td><td><code>4s</code></td><td>Duration of one full hue cycle.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="reveal">
  <h2>data-reveal</h2>
  <p>Word-by-word or line-by-line entrance animation. Text slides up and fades in with staggered timing when scrolled into view.</p>

  <browser-window src="/docs/examples/demos/reveal-basic.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/reveal" title="Text Reveal" shadow></browser-window>

  <code-block language="html" label="Text reveal">{{ revealCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-reveal</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"word"</code>, <code>"line"</code></td><td>Split mode. Default is word.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-reveal-delay</code></td><td>ms</td><td>Stagger delay between chunks (default 80).</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-reveal-duration</code></td><td>ms</td><td>Animation duration per chunk (default 400).</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="scramble">
  <h2>data-scramble <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">effects</span></h2>
  <p>Characters resolve left-to-right from random symbols. Think Hollywood decryption or sci-fi terminal output. Triggers on scroll.</p>

  <browser-window src="/docs/examples/demos/scramble-basic.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/scramble" title="Text Scramble" shadow></browser-window>

  <code-block language="html" label="Text scramble">{{ scrambleCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-scramble</code></td><td>ms</td><td>Total duration. Default is 1500ms.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-scramble-chars</code></td><td>string</td><td>Character set for random chars (default: <code>!&lt;&gt;-_\\/[]&#123;&#125;=+*^?#</code>).</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-scramble-speed</code></td><td>ms</td><td>Frame interval. Default is 30ms.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="shimmer">
  <h2>data-shimmer</h2>
  <p>CSS-only shimmering highlight that sweeps across the text on a loop.</p>

  <browser-window src="/docs/examples/demos/shimmer-basic.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/shimmer" title="Shimmer Text" shadow></browser-window>

  <code-block language="html" label="Shimmer text">{{ shimmerCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-shimmer</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"slow"</code>, <code>"fast"</code></td><td>Speed preset. Default is 2s cycle.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="sparkle">
  <h2>data-sparkle <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">kawaii</span></h2>
  <p>CSS-only floating sparkle stars. Two &#x2726; characters orbit the element with staggered float animations &mdash; one gold at top-right, one lavender at bottom-left.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Sparkle">{{ sparkleCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-sparkle</code></td><td>boolean</td><td>Adds floating sparkle stars via pseudo-elements.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section id="stamp">
  <h2>data-stamp <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">retro</span></h2>
  <p>Rubber stamp effect with fractal noise SVG filter, rotation, and <code>mix-blend-mode: multiply</code>. Requires JS for the SVG filter injection.</p>
  <code-block language="html" label="Stamp">{{ stampCode | escape }}</code-block>
  <h3>Attributes</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-stamp</code></td><td><code>""</code>, <code>"red"</code>, <code>"blue"</code>, <code>"green"</code>, <code>"black"</code>, <code>"gold"</code></td><td>Ink color preset. Empty defaults to red.</td></tr>
      <tr><td>(modifier) <code>straight</code></td><td>space-separated</td><td>No rotation (0deg).</td></tr>
      <tr><td>(modifier) <code>slight</code></td><td>space-separated</td><td>Slight rotation (-2deg).</td></tr>
      <tr><td>(modifier) <code>heavy</code></td><td>space-separated</td><td>Heavy rotation (-8deg).</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
